WEBVTT

01:30.950 --> 01:35.020
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.640 --> 01:36.310
Something this serious had happened,

01:35.780 --> 01:39.520
[2022]

01:36.310 --> 01:37.759
but why didn't you report it to me?

01:37.759 --> 01:39.150
You just made the call yourself.

01:39.150 --> 01:39.789
Are you the team leader,

01:39.789 --> 01:40.509
or am I?

01:40.800 --> 01:42.130
They were going too far!

01:42.560 --> 01:43.759
I just gave them
a taste of their own medicine

01:43.759 --> 01:45.020
to teach them a lesson.

01:45.479 --> 01:46.009
Besides,

01:46.310 --> 01:47.070
this won't affect the work,

01:47.070 --> 01:47.759
will it?

01:47.950 --> 01:49.039
Of course it matters.

01:49.039 --> 01:50.150
If you don't handle relationships well,

01:50.150 --> 01:51.410
it will have an impact.

01:51.840 --> 01:52.710
If it does,

01:52.870 --> 01:54.070
I'll just quit, okay?

02:00.640 --> 02:02.560
Young people are really
reforming the workplace, huh?

02:02.560 --> 02:03.090
Mr. Wang.

02:04.330 --> 02:05.400
Actually, sometimes,

02:05.400 --> 02:06.040
you should learn from

02:06.040 --> 02:06.840
them today.

02:07.790 --> 02:09.449
Don't be too hard on yourself.

02:13.650 --> 02:16.930
[Episode 29] [An Eye for an Eye]

02:18.590 --> 02:19.680
Fellow workers,

02:19.910 --> 02:20.910
listen, we...

02:20.910 --> 02:22.520
do have some problems here.

02:22.680 --> 02:24.190
But the management

02:24.190 --> 02:25.870
is already working on a solution.

02:25.870 --> 02:26.960
Look, well,

02:26.960 --> 02:27.560
just sitting around here

02:27.560 --> 02:28.400
isn't the way.

02:35.430 --> 02:36.430
This has nothing to do with me.

02:36.430 --> 02:38.030
I tried to talk them out of it.

02:39.910 --> 02:41.110
Listen up, everyone.

02:42.000 --> 02:43.190
If you don't want to work,

02:43.190 --> 02:44.650
get your pay and leave now.

02:45.520 --> 02:47.160
Let me talk to them. Let me talk to them.

02:47.160 --> 02:48.720
Hey, fellow workers,

02:48.750 --> 02:49.960
which other construction site

02:49.960 --> 02:51.310
treats you better than here? Right?

02:51.310 --> 02:53.170
Let's just get back to work, okay?

02:53.430 --> 02:54.030
Liu, Liu.

02:54.280 --> 02:54.680
Dali.

02:54.680 --> 02:55.560
Hurry up.

02:56.079 --> 02:57.190
Let's go.

02:57.360 --> 02:58.400
Let's go.

03:00.630 --> 03:01.160
Xiaolan.

03:03.150 --> 03:05.150
Something happened at the bank too?

03:05.590 --> 03:06.150
Yes.

03:06.430 --> 03:07.430
Not just the bank,

03:07.520 --> 03:08.600
but also the Haihua Hotel

03:08.600 --> 03:10.060
and the Golden Sands Pool.

03:10.240 --> 03:12.100
It seems this coordinated attack

03:12.240 --> 03:13.360
is targeting me.

03:14.680 --> 03:16.910
The materials center can provide 700,000.

03:16.910 --> 03:17.680
My personal savings

03:17.680 --> 03:18.680
can add a bit more.

03:19.000 --> 03:20.130
Right, and mine too.

03:20.310 --> 03:22.170
We can scrape together a million.

03:22.590 --> 03:23.590
Yeah, yeah.

03:23.870 --> 03:24.710
As for me,

03:25.030 --> 03:26.280
the balance from the Haihua Hotel

03:26.280 --> 03:27.400
hasn't been paid yet,

03:27.400 --> 03:29.280
and the workers haven't been paid.

03:29.280 --> 03:30.800
But I can go back and ask Fengmei

03:30.800 --> 03:31.630
to see how much money

03:31.630 --> 03:33.360
we can scrape together at home.

03:33.430 --> 03:35.230
I can come up with more this time.

03:35.910 --> 03:37.910
I should have 1.5 million.

03:38.280 --> 03:39.120
Tell me in advance,

03:39.120 --> 03:40.720
and I'll get the money ready.

03:42.190 --> 03:42.650
Come in.

03:47.360 --> 03:47.910
Ms. Xia,

03:48.320 --> 03:49.810
my colleagues just told me

03:49.840 --> 03:51.680
that they can skip
their salaries this month.

03:51.680 --> 03:52.800
They can wait until the company's finances

03:52.800 --> 03:53.680
improve.

03:56.840 --> 03:58.470
Please thank everyone for me.

03:58.470 --> 04:00.800
Salaries will be paid as usual this month.

04:00.920 --> 04:02.150
I can handle my own problems.

04:02.150 --> 04:04.150
There's no need for you all to worry.

04:04.360 --> 04:05.160
Okay, Ms. Xia.

04:05.560 --> 04:06.560
I'll head out now.

04:06.680 --> 04:07.810
Thanks to everyone.

04:07.840 --> 04:08.700
It's all right.

04:13.400 --> 04:15.400
I know everyone is worried about me.

04:15.800 --> 04:17.240
But the hole we're in

04:17.310 --> 04:18.430
is just too big.

04:18.950 --> 04:19.920
Even if all of you

04:19.920 --> 04:21.190
went bankrupt,

04:21.269 --> 04:22.720
it wouldn't be enough to pay it back.

04:22.720 --> 04:24.120
And you are my safety net.

04:24.390 --> 04:26.160
I can't destroy that, can I?

04:26.680 --> 04:27.240
Xiaolan,

04:27.270 --> 04:29.000
you have to listen to me on this.

04:29.120 --> 04:30.120
If the bank

04:30.120 --> 04:31.520
really demands payment,

04:31.680 --> 04:32.600
everyone here

04:33.070 --> 04:34.870
can scrape together a little bit

04:35.070 --> 04:36.070
to pay them back.

04:36.120 --> 04:37.000
You don't want the bank

04:37.000 --> 04:37.800
to really take

04:37.920 --> 04:40.520
your Golden Sands Pool
to be auctioned, right?

04:40.560 --> 04:41.310
Stay calm.

04:41.480 --> 04:42.390
Aren't we trying

04:42.390 --> 04:43.990
to figure out a way together?

04:44.720 --> 04:45.600
Xiaolan.

04:46.430 --> 04:47.950
Regarding the financial issues,

04:47.950 --> 04:49.350
I don't understand much,

04:49.680 --> 04:51.270
so I can't be of much help.

04:52.120 --> 04:53.560
But regarding Nie Weiguo suing you

04:53.560 --> 04:55.040
for plagiarism,

04:55.430 --> 04:56.630
what do you plan to do?

04:57.270 --> 04:58.159
As far as I know,

04:58.480 --> 05:00.390
he has already prepared

05:00.390 --> 05:01.750
the original design drafts.

05:01.750 --> 05:03.310
But everyone is well aware

05:03.310 --> 05:03.950
and knows clearly

05:03.950 --> 05:05.310
that they must be fake.

05:05.630 --> 05:08.630
But can current technology analyze

05:08.830 --> 05:10.240
which is the original draft

05:10.240 --> 05:11.440
and which is the copy?

05:13.320 --> 05:14.580
Mr. Mao, you're right.

05:15.000 --> 05:16.850
Based on our law firm's experience,

05:16.850 --> 05:18.160
the difficulty of copyright cases

05:18.160 --> 05:19.090
lies right here.

05:19.240 --> 05:20.600
With current technology,

05:20.600 --> 05:21.430
there is simply no way

05:21.430 --> 05:22.390
to accurately judge

05:22.390 --> 05:23.920
the creation time of the design drafts.

05:23.920 --> 05:25.050
Plus, Hou Qi

05:25.160 --> 05:27.070
indeed served as Nie Weiguo's assistant.

05:27.070 --> 05:28.400
Logically speaking...

05:29.750 --> 05:31.800
there is a possibility of plagiarism.

05:31.800 --> 05:32.930
Then how do we judge?

05:33.190 --> 05:33.990
Connections?

05:34.390 --> 05:35.070
Seniority?

05:35.830 --> 05:37.030
Then young designers

05:37.120 --> 05:39.780
would be at a huge disadvantage,
wouldn't they?

05:40.120 --> 05:41.180
Mr. Mao, calm down.

05:41.920 --> 05:43.390
Future judicial appraisal technology

05:43.390 --> 05:44.430
will definitely advance rapidly.

05:44.430 --> 05:45.270
In the future, none of this

05:45.270 --> 05:46.270
will be a problem.

05:46.680 --> 05:47.600
As for now,

05:48.000 --> 05:49.060
we will definitely

05:49.159 --> 05:50.360
fight for fairness.

05:51.040 --> 05:52.570
This isn't just for Xiaolan

05:52.920 --> 05:53.680
but also for

05:53.680 --> 05:55.680
more young designers in the future.

06:01.190 --> 06:01.680
Hello?

06:03.600 --> 06:04.390
Uncle Tang.

06:05.120 --> 06:06.800
So much has happened recently.

06:06.800 --> 06:08.530
Don't you want to talk about it?

06:09.430 --> 06:10.160
Right now,

06:10.160 --> 06:11.160
we are one.

06:11.630 --> 06:13.000
No matter how much
you try to avoid suspicion,

06:13.000 --> 06:14.200
in the eyes of others,

06:14.220 --> 06:15.220
we are one.

06:16.000 --> 06:17.480
Since we are one,

06:17.830 --> 06:18.830
we share the same fate.

06:18.830 --> 06:19.960
We are inseparable.

06:20.390 --> 06:20.920
Xiaolan,

06:21.310 --> 06:22.570
you're a smart person.

06:22.680 --> 06:23.950
Am I making myself clear?

06:23.950 --> 06:24.750
I understand.

06:25.360 --> 06:26.870
It's just that I'm...

06:27.830 --> 06:29.230
A bit unaccustomed to it?

06:30.430 --> 06:31.120
Not used to

06:31.270 --> 06:32.150
having someone

06:32.550 --> 06:33.670
cover for you now?

06:34.430 --> 06:36.290
Then you'll have to get used to it.

06:37.240 --> 06:38.440
But by the same token,

06:38.480 --> 06:39.880
given our relationship,

06:40.190 --> 06:41.630
there will be many eyes

06:41.830 --> 06:42.630
watching you,

06:42.830 --> 06:43.950
so you must be even more careful

06:43.950 --> 06:45.280
not to make a wrong move.

06:45.480 --> 06:46.140
Uncle Tang,

06:46.190 --> 06:46.990
rest assured.

06:47.190 --> 06:48.650
Every procedure at Qi Hang

06:48.680 --> 06:50.680
was done according to regulations.

06:52.310 --> 06:54.920
I believe you've been following the rules.

06:55.950 --> 06:56.920
But right now,

06:57.159 --> 06:58.000
everything

06:58.240 --> 06:59.240
is coming at once.

06:59.430 --> 07:00.430
What you need to do

07:00.630 --> 07:01.870
is stay very calm.

07:04.190 --> 07:05.560
Regarding the bank,

07:05.680 --> 07:07.140
I've asked around for you.

07:07.430 --> 07:08.950
As for the early repayment,

07:08.950 --> 07:11.040
the bank won't make a decision
immediately.

07:11.040 --> 07:11.480
So,

07:11.630 --> 07:13.030
there is still some time.

07:13.270 --> 07:14.310
The most important thing now

07:14.310 --> 07:15.910
is this plagiarism lawsuit.

07:16.160 --> 07:17.950
If the plagiarism issue

07:17.950 --> 07:18.880
can be resolved,

07:19.000 --> 07:19.730
then the loan

07:19.870 --> 07:21.130
will be easily solved.

07:22.950 --> 07:23.510
However,

07:23.750 --> 07:24.810
with your ability,

07:25.040 --> 07:26.500
do you already have a plan?

07:27.510 --> 07:28.720
If you need anything,

07:28.950 --> 07:30.390
you can come to me anytime.

07:30.390 --> 07:31.310
I will,

07:32.150 --> 07:33.190
as a family member,

07:33.190 --> 07:34.390
give you some advice.

07:34.560 --> 07:34.890
Okay.

07:35.120 --> 07:35.480
Okay.

07:35.600 --> 07:37.130
The meal is ready. Come eat.

07:37.240 --> 07:37.970
Let's go eat.

07:39.040 --> 07:40.120
Look at these 2 drawings.

07:40.120 --> 07:41.260
The strokes are obviously different.

07:41.260 --> 07:41.950
I'll go compare them.

07:41.950 --> 07:42.310
Okay.

07:49.720 --> 07:50.320
Ms. Hou Qi,

07:50.560 --> 07:51.190
here are the drawings you wanted.

07:51.190 --> 07:51.870
Thanks.

07:54.000 --> 07:54.360
Okay,

07:54.380 --> 07:55.980
I'll contact him right away.

07:59.950 --> 08:01.750
Hello, this is Qi Hang Property.

08:03.510 --> 08:04.190
See you tomorrow.

08:04.190 --> 08:05.120
See you tomorrow.

08:05.120 --> 08:05.580
I'm off.

08:06.920 --> 08:07.920
See you tomorrow.

08:08.070 --> 08:08.800
See you tomorrow, Ms. Xia.

08:08.800 --> 08:09.130
Okay.

08:09.190 --> 08:09.600
Bye-bye.

08:09.600 --> 08:11.000
See you. See you. See you.

08:11.430 --> 08:12.160
Hou Qi, look.

08:13.720 --> 08:15.560
These are completely different.

08:15.560 --> 08:16.290
Look at this.

08:17.190 --> 08:17.720
These 2.

08:18.310 --> 08:19.680
These 2 obviously have
the same drawing style

08:19.680 --> 08:20.560
by the same person.

08:20.560 --> 08:21.240
Look at this part.

08:21.240 --> 08:21.600
Yes.

08:24.680 --> 08:26.000
This one is clearly better.

08:26.000 --> 08:26.560
The pressure used—

08:26.560 --> 08:27.090
Alright.

08:27.160 --> 08:28.070
It's getting dark.

08:28.070 --> 08:29.130
Let's call it a day.

08:29.430 --> 08:30.360
Thanks for your hard work.

08:30.360 --> 08:31.960
I'll treat you to a good meal.

08:34.630 --> 08:35.270
San.

08:35.750 --> 08:36.200
San.

08:38.030 --> 08:38.559
Xiaolan.

08:39.240 --> 08:40.640
Zhenzhu told me about it.

08:41.010 --> 08:42.240
If there's anything I can help with,

08:42.240 --> 08:43.240
just say the word.

08:43.549 --> 08:44.610
Okay. Thanks, San.

08:44.910 --> 08:47.400
Actually, there is something
you can help with.

08:47.400 --> 08:48.450
Prepare a feast

08:48.480 --> 08:49.540
for my colleagues.

08:50.840 --> 08:51.770
Sure. Coming right up.

08:51.770 --> 08:53.500
-Okay. Have a seat.
-Thank you.

08:56.000 --> 08:56.910
Let me tell you,

08:57.300 --> 08:59.300
don't judge this place by its looks.

08:59.480 --> 09:00.000
The food here

09:00.000 --> 09:01.270
is just as good as big restaurants.

09:01.270 --> 09:02.440
I guarantee that after this time,

09:02.440 --> 09:03.440
you'll want to come back.

09:03.440 --> 09:04.900
Next is today's top story.

09:05.450 --> 09:06.510
After much preparation

09:06.510 --> 09:07.910
and a massive publicity campaign,

09:07.910 --> 09:10.440
Chengrong Electronics City
is about to open.

09:10.550 --> 09:14.350
But recently, it has been embroiled
in a design plagiarism scandal.

09:14.510 --> 09:15.030
Today,

09:15.320 --> 09:17.550
our reporter interviewed
one of the parties involved,

09:17.550 --> 09:19.870
Architect Mr. Nie Weiguo.

09:21.320 --> 09:22.320
Hello, everyone.

09:22.360 --> 09:23.860
I am from the Jiangcheng Design Institute,

09:23.860 --> 09:24.520
Nie Weiguo.

09:25.720 --> 09:27.030
He has the nerve to be interviewed?

09:27.030 --> 09:28.670
Thank you for accepting our interview.

09:28.670 --> 09:29.200
We see

09:29.200 --> 09:30.150
that public opinion suggests

09:30.150 --> 09:32.680
that Xia Xiaolan
is a young designer after all

09:32.790 --> 09:34.390
and should be given another chance.

09:34.390 --> 09:35.200
Why do you

09:35.240 --> 09:36.900
insist on taking her to court?

09:37.100 --> 09:38.960
This matter concerns
the integrity of the industry.

09:38.960 --> 09:40.490
It's a matter of principle.

09:40.870 --> 09:41.630
Actually,

09:41.840 --> 09:42.640
I am doing this

09:42.790 --> 09:44.240
to help these young people,

09:44.240 --> 09:45.900
to keep them on the right path.

09:46.080 --> 09:46.840
You know how it is.

09:46.840 --> 09:47.750
Young people these days,

09:47.750 --> 09:49.080
especially this kind of

09:49.390 --> 09:50.750
young girls

09:51.600 --> 09:53.320
who rely on their youth and beauty,

09:53.320 --> 09:54.650
want to take shortcuts.

09:55.840 --> 09:57.380
But has anyone thought about it?

09:57.380 --> 09:58.320
Chengrong Electronics City

09:58.320 --> 09:59.780
is such a massive project,

10:00.320 --> 10:01.380
and how did it end up

10:01.480 --> 10:03.210
with someone like Xia Xiaolan,

10:03.270 --> 10:04.510
who has very little

10:04.510 --> 10:06.360
design experience,

10:06.440 --> 10:07.840
a young female designer?

10:08.150 --> 10:10.010
I want to reiterate one more time.

10:10.420 --> 10:11.520
Your favorites.

10:11.550 --> 10:12.240
Thanks.

10:13.480 --> 10:15.140
In the face of such injustice,

10:15.320 --> 10:17.120
I can't pretend to be above it all.

10:17.120 --> 10:18.920
I'll play the villain this time.

10:19.000 --> 10:19.550
However,

10:20.030 --> 10:20.960
this kind of behavior

10:20.960 --> 10:22.090
can't be tolerated.

10:22.390 --> 10:24.550
What a hypocrite. I'm furious!

10:24.630 --> 10:25.270
Change the channel!

10:25.270 --> 10:25.750
Wait.

10:26.320 --> 10:27.670
Don't change the channel.

10:27.670 --> 10:28.240
Look.

10:28.510 --> 10:30.240
See how engrossed the people nearby are.

10:30.240 --> 10:31.150
Actually,

10:31.170 --> 10:32.570
it was quite unexpected.

10:33.030 --> 10:34.220
My main job is usually

10:34.220 --> 10:35.840
at the Jiangcheng Design Institute.

10:35.840 --> 10:36.480
I mostly deal with

10:36.480 --> 10:37.940
state-owned enterprises

10:37.960 --> 10:39.600
and public facility projects.

10:39.600 --> 10:40.900
I don't pay much attention

10:40.900 --> 10:42.330
to commercial projects.

10:42.630 --> 10:44.440
It was just a chance conversation

10:44.440 --> 10:44.910
with a friend in the industry...

10:44.910 --> 10:45.320
Hello?

10:46.630 --> 10:47.360
Xia Xiaolan.

10:47.630 --> 10:48.510
That jerk Nie Weiguo

10:48.510 --> 10:50.360
gave an interview. Do you know that?

10:50.360 --> 10:51.240
Isn't Zhou Cheng supposed to be

10:51.240 --> 10:52.240
a top law student?

10:52.510 --> 10:53.390
Did he buy his degree?

10:53.390 --> 10:54.520
He's doing nothing.

10:54.600 --> 10:55.670
We haven't even gone to court yet,

10:55.670 --> 10:57.080
and we've already lost the battle
of public opinion.

10:57.080 --> 10:58.320
You have to do an interview too.

10:58.320 --> 10:58.910
Right now,

10:58.910 --> 10:59.840
I'm calling the TV station.

10:59.840 --> 11:00.600
Du Zhaohui,

11:00.840 --> 11:01.720
can you stop

11:01.720 --> 11:02.840
causing trouble for me here?

11:02.840 --> 11:04.630
The court cares about evidence,

11:04.630 --> 11:05.750
not public opinion.

11:05.750 --> 11:06.960
Besides, I'm the defendant.

11:06.960 --> 11:08.790
I'm not even worried, so why are you?

11:08.790 --> 11:10.120
How can I not be worried?

11:10.390 --> 11:11.320
If this keeps up,

11:11.440 --> 11:12.720
my reputation will be ruined

11:12.720 --> 11:14.920
before my Electronics City even opens.

11:15.000 --> 11:16.150
My entire fortune and life

11:16.150 --> 11:17.390
have been invested in it.

11:17.390 --> 11:18.000
He claims

11:18.000 --> 11:20.320
that I plagiarized
his architectural design.

11:20.320 --> 11:21.320
It has nothing to do

11:21.320 --> 11:22.750
with Electronics City's operations.

11:22.750 --> 11:23.440
Besides,

11:23.870 --> 11:25.630
don't you think that after this ordeal,

11:25.630 --> 11:26.840
Electronics City is actually

11:26.840 --> 11:27.620
getting more attention?

11:27.620 --> 11:29.900
Or perhaps, Designer Xia Xiaolan...

11:31.030 --> 11:31.630
Then...

11:32.150 --> 11:33.750
if you don't do an interview,

11:34.200 --> 11:35.000
I can, right?

11:35.350 --> 11:36.120
Suit yourself. Bye-bye.

11:36.120 --> 11:38.240
Thank you for accepting our interview.

11:38.240 --> 11:38.670
As for the follow-up,

11:38.670 --> 11:40.240
we will also try to interview

11:40.240 --> 11:42.870
Chengrong Electronics City
and Ms. Xia Xiaolan,

11:42.870 --> 11:44.320
so that the audience can have

11:44.320 --> 11:46.270
a more comprehensive understanding
of the event.

11:46.270 --> 11:46.840
It's okay.

11:46.840 --> 11:47.270
Eat up.

11:49.150 --> 11:49.670
Ms. Xia,

11:50.080 --> 11:51.960
Mr. Zhou also said earlier

11:51.960 --> 11:53.200
that the creation time of the drafts

11:53.200 --> 11:54.330
was hard to confirm.

11:54.480 --> 11:55.870
Then is the method you mentioned

11:55.870 --> 11:56.510
feasible?

11:57.550 --> 11:58.840
Facing such injustice,

11:58.840 --> 12:00.030
I want to tell everyone

12:00.030 --> 12:01.440
that we must have the courage to resist.

12:01.440 --> 12:02.720
We must trust our laws.

12:03.200 --> 12:04.060
We must believe

12:04.080 --> 12:06.150
that justice is in the people's hearts.

12:06.150 --> 12:07.750
Nie Weiguo is right.

12:08.110 --> 12:09.720
We need to trust the law.

12:09.750 --> 12:11.680
Justice is in the people's hearts.

12:11.840 --> 12:12.440
Let's eat.

12:13.360 --> 12:13.820
Come on,

12:13.870 --> 12:14.600
have a taste.

12:15.080 --> 12:15.390
Eat.

12:18.360 --> 12:20.790
That concludes our interview
with Nie Weiguo.

12:20.790 --> 12:22.720
Regarding the progress of the case...

12:22.720 --> 12:24.120
Have you seen the report?

12:25.670 --> 12:26.080
Good.

12:26.750 --> 12:27.720
Then I'll make things

12:27.720 --> 12:28.480
even bigger.

12:33.510 --> 12:34.240
Based on my understanding

12:34.240 --> 12:35.750
of Nie Weiguo,

12:36.410 --> 12:38.070
he's bad, but he's not stupid.

12:39.080 --> 12:40.380
He knows better than anyone

12:40.380 --> 12:41.780
that Ms. Xia is innocent.

12:41.840 --> 12:42.670
Then why did he

12:42.670 --> 12:44.330
come all this way to frame her?

12:44.750 --> 12:46.750
I think he must have been on the take.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.770
If he isn't Ms. Xia's enemy,

12:49.320 --> 12:50.720
then he's Mr. Du's enemy.

12:51.440 --> 12:52.150
That's not something

12:52.150 --> 12:53.210
we can worry about.

12:53.630 --> 12:54.320
We just need

12:54.390 --> 12:55.440
to do our best to finish

12:55.440 --> 12:56.900
the work Ms. Xia assigned.

12:59.840 --> 13:01.200
I keep feeling like

13:02.120 --> 13:04.180
someone betrayed Ms. Xia and Qi Hang.

13:05.390 --> 13:06.870
How could those people know

13:06.870 --> 13:08.150
about Nie Weiguo?

13:09.590 --> 13:11.450
Aside from the seminar incident,

13:11.840 --> 13:13.440
there were no other grudges.

13:14.150 --> 13:15.720
It could only be someone close

13:15.720 --> 13:16.510
who leaked it.

13:16.510 --> 13:17.030
Right.

13:17.930 --> 13:18.840
Then we can check

13:18.840 --> 13:20.030
who has connections with people

13:20.030 --> 13:20.790
in Gangdao.

13:22.150 --> 13:23.350
I think that'll work.

13:26.870 --> 13:28.400
I'm home. See you tomorrow.

13:29.080 --> 13:29.670
See you.

13:36.080 --> 13:37.240
Could it be me?

13:48.480 --> 13:49.080
Recently,

13:49.550 --> 13:51.600
the case of plagiarism in the design
of Chengrong Electronics City...

13:51.600 --> 13:52.460
It's this woman.

13:52.460 --> 13:53.200
I bet she must

13:53.200 --> 13:54.080
have some personal connections

13:54.080 --> 13:55.140
behind the scenes.

13:55.480 --> 13:55.890
Exactly.

13:55.890 --> 13:56.820
Come on, cheers.

13:57.030 --> 13:57.440
Come on.

13:57.440 --> 13:58.410
The focus has shifted
from the plagiarism itself

13:58.410 --> 14:00.200
to Designer Xia Xiaolan...

14:01.200 --> 14:03.000
She's a bit too lucky, isn't she?

14:03.150 --> 14:04.550
She does whatever makes money.

14:04.550 --> 14:05.840
Unless she's clairvoyant,

14:05.840 --> 14:07.480
there's something fishy going on.

14:07.480 --> 14:08.930
But the root of this matter

14:08.930 --> 14:11.330
is still whether Xia Xiaolan plagiarized.

14:11.440 --> 14:12.750
Nie Weiguo has stated multiple times

14:12.750 --> 14:15.200
that Xia Xiaolan's
current design assistant, Hou Qi,

14:15.200 --> 14:16.600
used to work at his unit

14:17.150 --> 14:19.080
and therefore saw his drafts.

14:19.390 --> 14:22.080
Xia Xiaolan's side has consistently
refused interviews.

14:22.080 --> 14:22.870
The owner of Electronics City,

14:22.870 --> 14:25.000
Du Zhaohui, has stated multiple times

14:25.080 --> 14:26.390
that regarding Xia Xiaolan's
design process,

14:26.390 --> 14:27.520
he witnessed it all,

14:27.600 --> 14:29.550
and that Xia Xiaolan
could not have plagiarized.

14:29.550 --> 14:31.790
Nie Weiguo stated in a radio interview

14:32.200 --> 14:33.150
that young designers

14:33.150 --> 14:34.630
can't, just because they have
a boss's support,

14:34.630 --> 14:35.890
do whatever they want.

14:36.120 --> 14:37.500
If they are not punished,

14:37.500 --> 14:38.720
it will cause great harm

14:38.720 --> 14:39.870
to the entire industry.

14:39.600 --> 14:41.280
[Plagiarism Allegations]

14:40.240 --> 14:40.670
Previously,

14:40.670 --> 14:42.550
Du Zhaohui stated in an interview

14:41.280 --> 14:42.970
[over the Architectural Design
of Chengrong Electronics City]

14:42.720 --> 14:44.790
that he and Xia Xiaolan are the victims,

14:44.790 --> 14:47.480
and that Nie Weiguo
is making false accusations.

14:47.480 --> 14:48.140
Plagiarism

14:48.750 --> 14:50.080
is intellectual theft.

14:50.300 --> 14:51.330
I won't tolerate it.

14:51.330 --> 14:52.520
Mr. Du's reaction

14:52.550 --> 14:53.750
doesn't surprise me.

14:53.960 --> 14:55.390
He's playing the knight in shining armor.

14:55.390 --> 14:55.980
After all,

14:55.980 --> 14:57.440
he gave her such a massive project.

14:57.440 --> 14:59.080
He's bound to protect her to the end.

14:59.080 --> 14:59.870
However,

15:00.240 --> 15:01.870
I might have disrupted Mr. Du's

15:01.870 --> 15:03.360
plan to win a smile from a beauty.

15:03.360 --> 15:04.200
This Nie Weiguo

15:04.200 --> 15:05.550
is quite good at playing the victim.

15:05.550 --> 15:06.910
He portrays himself

15:06.910 --> 15:08.030
as an honest man,

15:08.240 --> 15:09.320
who, because he wasn't slick enough,

15:09.320 --> 15:10.440
gained no commercial benefits,

15:10.440 --> 15:11.440
like a workhorse.

15:12.870 --> 15:13.510
But you?

15:14.150 --> 15:15.200
A beneficiary

15:15.360 --> 15:17.160
who used your looks to get ahead.

15:17.360 --> 15:19.870
And you have an ambiguous relationship

15:20.030 --> 15:20.910
with Mr. Du

15:20.910 --> 15:21.930
of Chengrong Electronics City.

15:21.930 --> 15:24.190
Are you looking for trouble, Zhou Cheng?

15:24.960 --> 15:25.620
Seriously,

15:26.080 --> 15:27.550
the fact that the trial
is starting so soon

15:27.550 --> 15:28.150
shows that the other side

15:28.150 --> 15:29.480
has been planning this for a long time.

15:29.480 --> 15:31.270
I guess it started from the day

15:31.270 --> 15:32.390
construction began at Electronics City.

15:32.390 --> 15:34.080
Investor Du Zhaohui has repeatedly stated

15:34.080 --> 15:35.150
that he and Xia Xiaolan are the victims.

15:35.150 --> 15:35.610
Come in.

15:35.790 --> 15:37.030
And he accused Nie Weiguo...

15:37.030 --> 15:38.440
Ms. Xia, everything is ready.

15:38.440 --> 15:39.100
Currently,

15:39.150 --> 15:40.720
the other party involved, Xia Xiaolan,

15:40.720 --> 15:42.250
has refused all interviews

15:42.630 --> 15:44.560
and has not issued any statements.

15:44.720 --> 15:45.150
You may leave.

15:45.150 --> 15:47.480
This makes the case even more mysterious.

15:48.330 --> 15:49.360
Chengrong Electronics City

15:49.360 --> 15:51.120
is a key project in Shengcheng,

15:51.440 --> 15:52.550
aiming to build Asia's...

15:52.550 --> 15:53.410
Looking at him,

15:53.670 --> 15:54.550
I guess he has already

15:54.550 --> 15:55.810
realized his mistake.

15:56.840 --> 15:58.040
So you still choose

15:58.200 --> 15:59.660
to continue trusting him?

16:00.600 --> 16:01.670
But the plagiarism incident

16:01.670 --> 16:02.750
has cast a shadow

16:02.750 --> 16:04.000
over the future of Electronics City.

16:04.000 --> 16:04.910
The Electronics City side

16:04.910 --> 16:06.320
has not yet revealed if they

16:06.320 --> 16:07.840
will postpone the opening.

16:07.840 --> 16:08.970
I believe in the law,

16:10.120 --> 16:11.920
and I believe in my own judgment.

16:12.390 --> 16:13.550
The trial will begin tomorrow morning

16:13.550 --> 16:15.550
at the Shengcheng court.

16:15.720 --> 16:16.550
Why hasn't this female designer

16:16.550 --> 16:17.910
come out to speak yet?

16:18.030 --> 16:19.360
The trial is about to start.

16:19.360 --> 16:20.200
Exactly.

16:21.480 --> 16:23.430
[Shengcheng People's Court]

16:22.840 --> 16:23.270
Mr. Du,

16:23.390 --> 16:24.550
I heard that you and Xia Xiaolan

16:24.550 --> 16:25.360
are more than just

16:25.360 --> 16:26.600
employer and employee.

16:26.600 --> 16:27.360
Is the Electronics City project

16:27.360 --> 16:28.510
just a gift to promote her

16:28.510 --> 16:29.600
because you want to woo her?

16:29.600 --> 16:30.120
Regarding the plagiarism,

16:30.120 --> 16:31.120
did you use your resources

16:31.120 --> 16:31.960
and connections?

16:31.960 --> 16:32.670
Nonsense.

16:33.200 --> 16:34.630
This is a multi-million-yuan project.

16:34.630 --> 16:36.030
It's the largest electronics mall in Asia.

16:36.030 --> 16:37.320
And you say I used it to pick up girls?

16:37.320 --> 16:39.240
I am rich, but I'm not stupid.

16:39.600 --> 16:41.150
Did you take someone's money

16:41.150 --> 16:41.870
to write this rubbish?

16:41.870 --> 16:42.510
I wouldn't dare.

16:42.510 --> 16:42.960
Then Mr. Du,

16:42.960 --> 16:43.840
what exactly is going on between you two?

16:43.840 --> 16:44.960
Can you tell us?

16:45.220 --> 16:47.420
It's just a cooperative relationship.

16:48.600 --> 16:50.000
-The car...
-The car is here.

16:50.000 --> 16:50.930
The car, the car.

16:52.890 --> 16:53.710
Mr. Nie.

16:53.760 --> 16:54.720
-Mr. Nie.
-Mr. Nie.

16:54.720 --> 16:55.910
Can you say a few words to us?

16:55.910 --> 16:56.600
Say a few words, please.

16:56.600 --> 16:57.600
Look at that Nie Weiguo.

16:57.600 --> 16:58.660
Look how smug he is.

16:58.840 --> 16:59.390
I knew

16:59.390 --> 17:00.390
he was no good,

17:00.630 --> 17:02.030
doing such dirty things.

17:02.120 --> 17:03.440
And these people
are just blindly following along.

17:03.440 --> 17:04.200
Regarding today's trial,

17:04.200 --> 17:05.260
are you confident?

17:05.950 --> 17:06.780
Of course I am.

17:07.310 --> 17:08.480
Xiaolan said she has a way,

17:08.480 --> 17:09.790
and she'll make it work.

17:09.790 --> 17:10.790
Why isn't Xiaolan

17:10.790 --> 17:11.829
here yet?

17:11.829 --> 17:13.440
Yeah. She left very early,

17:13.440 --> 17:14.920
but why hasn't she arrived yet?

17:14.920 --> 17:16.250
She should be here soon.

17:16.720 --> 17:17.349
I'm actually

17:17.349 --> 17:18.510
quite calm.

17:27.000 --> 17:27.880
Xia Xiaolan is here!

17:27.880 --> 17:29.010
Xia Xiaolan is here!

17:39.270 --> 17:40.670
Which one is Xia Xiaolan?

17:40.880 --> 17:42.140
Is it that young woman?

17:42.440 --> 17:43.110
I was wondering,

17:43.110 --> 17:44.970
isn't there only one young woman?

17:45.510 --> 17:46.170
Watch this.

17:46.290 --> 17:47.210
My apprentice

17:47.240 --> 17:49.370
has come up with a surprise move again.

18:02.510 --> 18:04.240
There is only one truth.

18:13.880 --> 18:14.750
Why didn't Xiaolan come

18:14.750 --> 18:15.640
with them?

18:16.110 --> 18:16.960
This girl

18:17.590 --> 18:19.160
has one trick after another.

18:19.160 --> 18:19.830
Just watch.

18:23.200 --> 18:24.200
Hello, everyone.

18:24.440 --> 18:26.170
I'll take a moment of your time.

18:26.510 --> 18:27.960
These past few days, the media

18:27.960 --> 18:30.090
has been very concerned about my case.

18:30.310 --> 18:31.590
So, I have prepared

18:31.590 --> 18:33.070
a small gift for everyone.

18:34.960 --> 18:35.590
I forgot to introduce myself.

18:35.590 --> 18:36.300
Everyone gets one.

18:36.300 --> 18:37.480
I am the defendant in this case.

18:37.480 --> 18:38.070
Take a look, everyone.

18:38.070 --> 18:39.790
I'm Xia Xiaolan

18:39.920 --> 18:41.510
from Qi Hang Architectural Design Firm.

18:41.510 --> 18:42.790
Nice to meet you all.

18:49.030 --> 18:49.640
Mr. Du,

18:49.790 --> 18:50.640
why are there

18:50.640 --> 18:52.170
2 identical drawings here?

18:52.640 --> 18:53.240
Let me see.

18:53.880 --> 18:55.410
What does this mean, Mr. Du?

18:56.750 --> 18:57.510
I don't know either.

18:57.510 --> 18:57.920
Go.

18:58.590 --> 18:58.960
Here.

18:59.400 --> 18:59.750
Here.

19:02.500 --> 19:04.440
This one clearly belongs to Nie Weiguo.

19:04.440 --> 19:06.500
Xiaolan draws much better than this.

19:08.040 --> 19:08.930
Mr. Mao, look.

19:09.640 --> 19:10.880
When Xiaolan drew this last year,

19:10.880 --> 19:11.680
I-I saw it.

19:11.830 --> 19:13.630
Pass them around and take a look.

19:16.640 --> 19:17.680
Pass them around. Pass them around.

19:17.680 --> 19:18.200
Alright.

19:18.200 --> 19:20.030
These are the design drafts.

19:20.050 --> 19:20.910
Design drafts?

19:21.510 --> 19:22.200
But mine

19:22.200 --> 19:23.460
is different from yours.

19:23.460 --> 19:24.190
Look at mine.

19:24.400 --> 19:25.310
While Comrade Nie Weiguo

19:25.310 --> 19:27.030
was busy appearing on TV programs

19:27.030 --> 19:28.440
and complaining to the media

19:28.440 --> 19:30.100
about the injustice he faced,

19:30.350 --> 19:32.080
I certainly didn't sit idly by.

19:32.640 --> 19:34.310
But I don't intend to debate him

19:34.310 --> 19:35.170
on television.

19:35.510 --> 19:37.110
I believe designers

19:37.110 --> 19:38.270
should use other ways

19:38.270 --> 19:39.470
to prove themselves.

19:40.990 --> 19:42.470
As for who is lying

19:43.200 --> 19:45.060
and who appropriated whose work,

19:45.400 --> 19:46.720
the judge will decide.

19:47.880 --> 19:50.030
I believe there is no threshold

19:50.030 --> 19:51.560
for appreciating architectural works.

19:51.560 --> 19:53.470
Beauty is an intuitive feeling.

19:54.940 --> 19:56.110
What you have now

19:56.110 --> 19:57.550
are all the works
by Comrade Nie Weiguo and me

19:57.550 --> 19:59.280
since the start of our careers.

19:59.960 --> 20:00.750
For these works,

20:00.750 --> 20:01.960
I deliberately didn't label

20:01.960 --> 20:03.090
the authors' names.

20:03.540 --> 20:04.950
I want to invite everyone

20:05.030 --> 20:05.920
to play a game

20:06.510 --> 20:07.200
to guess

20:07.440 --> 20:08.920
which ones are my works

20:09.440 --> 20:11.440
and which are Nie Weiguo's.

20:18.290 --> 20:19.030
Where did she get

20:19.030 --> 20:20.560
so many of my design drafts?

20:22.240 --> 20:23.700
Look at Nie Weiguo's face.

20:24.400 --> 20:25.460
He must be furious.

20:43.380 --> 20:44.400
You've all received

20:44.400 --> 20:45.640
the materials, right?

20:45.640 --> 20:47.170
The trial is about to start.

20:47.200 --> 20:48.750
In the meantime, you can

20:48.750 --> 20:50.750
take a good look at these materials.

20:50.880 --> 20:52.550
Score them in your mind

20:52.790 --> 20:53.920
and make a judgment.

20:53.920 --> 20:55.680
When the verdict comes out,

20:55.880 --> 20:56.790
see if it matches

20:56.790 --> 20:57.680
what you think.

20:58.270 --> 20:59.070
I believe

20:59.440 --> 21:01.000
the court will deliver

21:01.270 --> 21:03.160
a fair and just judgment.

21:03.550 --> 21:04.310
I also welcome

21:04.310 --> 21:05.440
everyone here today

21:05.550 --> 21:06.950
to judge for themselves.

21:07.350 --> 21:07.920
Today,

21:08.160 --> 21:09.680
everyone has a say.

21:11.000 --> 21:11.590
See?

21:11.920 --> 21:13.880
That's my apprentice, Xia Xiaolan.

21:13.880 --> 21:16.280
She doesn't back down
or take any nonsense.

21:17.510 --> 21:18.920
Say a few more words, Ms. Xia!

21:18.920 --> 21:20.650
Ms. Xia, please say something!

21:25.760 --> 21:27.540
[Presiding Judge]

21:29.030 --> 21:31.030
We request that the defendant,
Xia Xiaolan,

21:31.030 --> 21:32.680
and Chengrong Electronics City Plaza,

21:32.680 --> 21:34.640
immediately cease their infringing acts.

21:34.640 --> 21:35.310
Xia Xiaolan

21:35.350 --> 21:37.200
must publicly

21:37.200 --> 21:37.960
apologize to my client,

21:37.960 --> 21:39.510
pay RMB 200,000

21:39.880 --> 21:41.640
for mental and reputational damages,

21:41.640 --> 21:43.790
and bear all litigation costs.

21:44.200 --> 21:44.790
The defendant denies

21:44.790 --> 21:46.830
all accusations made by the plaintiff.

21:46.830 --> 21:48.510
The creation time of these 2 drafts

21:48.510 --> 21:49.440
is very close.

21:49.790 --> 21:51.070
With current technology,

21:51.070 --> 21:52.550
we can't accurately determine

21:52.550 --> 21:53.750
when they were drawn.

21:54.350 --> 21:55.280
Nie Weiguo?

21:55.510 --> 21:56.570
Never heard of him.

21:57.000 --> 21:58.720
From start to finish,
our Electronics City project

21:58.720 --> 21:59.790
was entrusted only to Xia Xiaolan

21:59.790 --> 22:00.640
and Qi Hang.

22:01.410 --> 22:03.240
Did you work
at the Jiangcheng Design Institute

22:03.240 --> 22:04.030
for 2 years?

22:04.350 --> 22:04.830
Yes.

22:05.240 --> 22:06.030
Were you

22:06.030 --> 22:07.830
Nie Weiguo's assistant at the time?

22:07.830 --> 22:09.550
Did you have access to all of Nie Weiguo's

22:09.550 --> 22:10.400
drafts?

22:10.880 --> 22:11.310
Yes,

22:11.510 --> 22:12.000
but I didn't—

22:12.000 --> 22:13.240
You only need to answer yes

22:13.240 --> 22:13.750
or no.

22:18.720 --> 22:19.160
Yes.

22:19.960 --> 22:22.240
You and Hou Qi are university alumni.

22:23.070 --> 22:24.870
Did you introduce her to Qi Hang?

22:25.160 --> 22:25.590
Yes.

22:26.200 --> 22:27.130
It is understood

22:27.160 --> 22:29.310
that when you introduced her to Qi Hang,

22:29.310 --> 22:30.400
Hou Qi had not yet

22:30.400 --> 22:32.360
resigned from the Jiangcheng Design Firm.

22:32.360 --> 22:33.760
Did you invite her

22:33.790 --> 22:34.920
solely because you valued

22:34.920 --> 22:36.000
her professional ability,

22:36.000 --> 22:38.270
or to take advantage
of her previous position?

22:38.270 --> 22:39.270
Is your relationship with her

22:39.270 --> 22:41.000
merely that of classmates?

22:41.270 --> 22:41.860
I object.

22:42.920 --> 22:43.440
This is entirely

22:43.440 --> 22:45.350
speculation by the plaintiff's lawyer.

22:45.350 --> 22:46.130
The witness

22:46.270 --> 22:47.960
need not answer that question.

22:47.960 --> 22:49.290
Defendant Xia Xiaolan,

22:49.440 --> 22:50.200
regarding Hou Qi,

22:50.200 --> 22:52.110
was it before or after

22:52.270 --> 22:53.550
the Electronics City project
that she joined

22:53.550 --> 22:55.240
Qi Hang Architectural Design Firm?

22:55.240 --> 22:57.680
It was before
the Electronics City project.

22:57.680 --> 22:58.750
In other words,

22:58.830 --> 23:00.720
you judged whether Hou Qi was qualified

23:00.720 --> 23:01.850
for the job at Qi Hang

23:01.890 --> 23:03.040
mainly based on

23:03.070 --> 23:04.440
her past work experience,

23:04.440 --> 23:05.920
specifically,

23:05.920 --> 23:06.750
at the Jiangcheng Design Institute,

23:06.750 --> 23:07.200
right?

23:08.070 --> 23:08.510
Yes.

23:09.000 --> 23:10.310
Then can we

23:10.350 --> 23:11.790
reasonably speculate

23:12.030 --> 23:13.720
that among the works used to demonstrate

23:13.720 --> 23:15.520
Hou Qi's professional ability,

23:15.750 --> 23:17.090
perhaps there was this work

23:17.090 --> 23:19.090
now suspected of plagiarism?

23:19.790 --> 23:20.310
I don't think

23:20.310 --> 23:21.640
there is a necessary connection.

23:21.640 --> 23:23.030
The expert just stated

23:23.640 --> 23:25.110
that current judicial appraisal technology

23:25.110 --> 23:26.160
can't determine

23:26.160 --> 23:28.280
the specific time the drafts were created.

23:28.280 --> 23:28.870
Then,

23:29.030 --> 23:30.270
can we

23:30.270 --> 23:32.000
further reasonably speculate

23:32.200 --> 23:33.480
that you exploited

23:33.510 --> 23:34.790
the limitations of technology

23:34.790 --> 23:36.440
to boldly plagiarize

23:36.550 --> 23:38.160
what Hou Qi provided to you,

23:38.160 --> 23:39.510
the plaintiff Nie Weiguo's

23:39.510 --> 23:40.840
architectural design?

23:41.400 --> 23:42.440
I object to the opposing counsel's

23:42.440 --> 23:43.640
line of questioning.

23:45.980 --> 23:47.400
The opposing counsel's speculation

23:47.400 --> 23:48.480
seems logical,

23:48.830 --> 23:50.290
but the premise is flawed.

23:50.540 --> 23:51.620
All of the above speculation

23:51.620 --> 23:53.790
is based entirely
on the assumption that Nie Weiguo

23:53.790 --> 23:55.110
was capable of designing a work

23:55.110 --> 23:56.640
like Chengrong Electronics City.

23:56.640 --> 23:57.270
And that

23:57.790 --> 23:59.050
is simply impossible.

24:04.110 --> 24:06.240
We request leave to call a new witness.

24:06.440 --> 24:06.970
Granted.

24:09.640 --> 24:10.880
The details are clearly much better.

24:10.880 --> 24:11.480
Look here.

24:11.680 --> 24:13.480
It doesn't even look like a copy.

24:14.350 --> 24:14.790
Look,

24:14.880 --> 24:16.310
this one is obviously Xia Xiaolan's.

24:16.310 --> 24:17.200
Look at the strokes.

24:17.200 --> 24:18.680
They're obviously from a woman.

24:18.680 --> 24:19.750
Look at this one I have.

24:19.750 --> 24:20.610
It's so simple.

24:20.610 --> 24:22.240
I feel like even I could draw it.

24:22.240 --> 24:22.720
These 2

24:22.750 --> 24:24.110
are obviously very different.

24:24.110 --> 24:25.200
-Yeah.
-Right?

24:36.720 --> 24:37.640
Doesn't he

24:37.640 --> 24:38.880
have beef with Mao Kangshan?

24:38.880 --> 24:39.880
How did he get him here?

24:39.880 --> 24:40.810
Professor Ning.

24:41.510 --> 24:42.400
You are a leading figure

24:42.400 --> 24:44.800
in our country's architectural industry.

24:44.920 --> 24:45.830
Everyone knows the title

24:45.830 --> 24:47.630
"Northern Ning, Southern Mao."

24:47.720 --> 24:49.550
Even in the global architectural industry,

24:49.550 --> 24:51.410
you enjoy a very high reputation.

24:51.590 --> 24:52.790
Now, my client

24:53.000 --> 24:55.260
would like you to evaluate 2 portfolios.

24:55.680 --> 24:57.640
Do you agree and promise

24:57.790 --> 24:59.190
to make a truthful, fair,

24:59.350 --> 25:00.950
and professional judgment?

25:01.000 --> 25:01.720
I agree.

25:13.640 --> 25:14.510
You won.

25:15.790 --> 25:16.590
You let me win.

25:17.960 --> 25:19.720
You know, although Nie Weiguo

25:20.030 --> 25:21.400
is a scumbag,

25:22.200 --> 25:23.350
he still made it

25:23.350 --> 25:26.240
to the position
of Vice President of the design institute.

25:26.240 --> 25:28.440
In the entire architectural industry,

25:28.880 --> 25:30.880
only you and I are qualified

25:31.200 --> 25:32.640
to judge him.

25:33.400 --> 25:35.680
Since I am a consultant for Qi Hang,

25:35.680 --> 25:37.010
I have to recuse myself.

25:37.720 --> 25:39.000
So today,

25:39.480 --> 25:42.240
I swallowed my pride to ask for your help.

25:42.920 --> 25:44.310
I've heard about

25:44.310 --> 25:45.840
this lawsuit in Jingcheng.

25:46.110 --> 25:47.590
If I can help the judge

25:47.750 --> 25:49.280
make the correct judgment,

25:49.590 --> 25:50.720
I am duty-bound.

25:51.680 --> 25:53.280
But let me state beforehand:

25:54.550 --> 25:56.150
I will seek truth from facts.

25:56.640 --> 25:58.400
You haven't changed a bit,

25:59.160 --> 26:01.000
always preaching with your big principles.

26:01.000 --> 26:02.680
Your words are watertight.

26:03.510 --> 26:04.720
I might trick you,

26:05.480 --> 26:07.240
but I'd never trick myself.

26:08.510 --> 26:09.310
When you see

26:09.310 --> 26:10.700
both of their drafts,

26:10.790 --> 26:12.830
you'll naturally understand.

26:14.590 --> 26:16.440
Aren't you the same as always?

26:17.070 --> 26:18.270
Protecting your own.

26:18.590 --> 26:19.590
For so many years,

26:20.030 --> 26:21.000
you have never

26:21.000 --> 26:23.000
taken the initiative to contact me.

26:23.400 --> 26:24.070
This time,

26:24.440 --> 26:25.310
if Xia Xiaolan

26:25.310 --> 26:26.770
weren't your apprentice,

26:27.000 --> 26:28.350
would you be so concerned

26:28.350 --> 26:29.750
and run around like this?

26:31.400 --> 26:31.830
Yes.

26:32.880 --> 26:33.720
I don't deny

26:33.720 --> 26:35.480
Xia Xiaolan is my apprentice.

26:36.200 --> 26:39.060
But I absolutely do not mean
to shield her unfairly.

26:39.510 --> 26:40.350
I've watched this project

26:40.350 --> 26:42.200
from start to finish.

26:43.160 --> 26:46.000
If I just watch facts

26:46.160 --> 26:48.110
being distorted like this,

26:49.110 --> 26:50.040
Professor Ning,

26:50.480 --> 26:51.770
then what future

26:52.000 --> 26:54.060
does our architectural circle have?

26:56.960 --> 26:58.400
Still,

26:59.550 --> 27:01.080
I'll seek truth from facts.

27:10.480 --> 27:12.160
Between the plaintiff and the defendant,

27:12.160 --> 27:12.830
as to who has the ability

27:12.830 --> 27:14.490
to create such original work,

27:14.590 --> 27:15.310
please use your professional knowledge

27:15.310 --> 27:16.110
to make

27:16.880 --> 27:17.550
a judgment.

27:18.160 --> 27:18.590
Okay.

27:20.070 --> 27:21.400
Objectively speaking,

27:22.030 --> 27:23.830
the original draft and the copy,

27:24.180 --> 27:26.310
in terms of forensic identification,

27:26.590 --> 27:29.250
are very difficult
to distinguish accurately.

27:29.590 --> 27:30.270
But

27:30.480 --> 27:32.470
if you have enough

27:32.470 --> 27:34.000
professional experience,

27:34.200 --> 27:35.930
it is entirely possible to make

27:36.070 --> 27:37.400
an accurate judgment.

27:38.790 --> 27:39.480
Today,

27:40.160 --> 27:40.960
I

27:41.680 --> 27:44.030
will venture to give this judgment.

27:44.720 --> 27:46.450
Chengrong Electronics City's

27:46.480 --> 27:48.750
original architectural designer

27:49.640 --> 27:50.790
is undoubtedly...

27:56.030 --> 27:56.760
Xia Xiaolan.

28:09.920 --> 28:10.480
They're coming out!

28:10.480 --> 28:11.620
It's open! It's open!

28:11.620 --> 28:12.600
Mr. Nie! Mr. Nie!

28:13.000 --> 28:13.720
Who won?

28:13.720 --> 28:14.480
Was there no verdict in court?

28:14.480 --> 28:16.270
We absolutely do not
accept the trial results.

28:16.270 --> 28:16.960
My client

28:16.960 --> 28:18.000
will continue to appeal.

28:18.000 --> 28:18.680
Please make way, everyone.

28:18.680 --> 28:19.980
Where is Xia Xiaolan?
Where is Xia Xiaolan?

28:19.980 --> 28:20.500
Ms. Xia.

28:20.720 --> 28:21.830
Ms. Xia! Ms. Xia!

28:21.960 --> 28:23.160
How do you feel, Ms. Xia?

28:23.160 --> 28:24.590
I am grateful for judicial justice.

28:24.590 --> 28:25.590
They dismissed

28:25.590 --> 28:26.570
Nie Weiguo's lawsuit on the spot,

28:26.570 --> 28:27.830
proving my innocence.

28:27.890 --> 28:28.790
What is real can't be fake,

28:28.790 --> 28:29.880
and what is fake can't be real.

28:29.880 --> 28:31.450
In the future, I'll continue to work hard

28:31.450 --> 28:32.310
to design more

28:32.310 --> 28:33.440
influential works.

28:33.550 --> 28:34.150
Thank you.

28:34.880 --> 28:36.390
Electronics City will open soon.

28:36.390 --> 28:37.510
Everyone is welcome to come see

28:37.510 --> 28:38.640
Xia Xiaolan's design

28:38.640 --> 28:40.970
and buy your favorite products, alright?

28:42.200 --> 28:42.750
Ms. Xia!

28:42.920 --> 28:44.240
Ms. Xia, say a few more words!

28:44.240 --> 28:45.240
Dean Nie, hold on.

28:51.640 --> 28:52.240
What is it?

28:52.480 --> 28:53.880
Is there something else?

28:54.200 --> 28:54.960
You lost the lawsuit,

28:54.960 --> 28:56.290
and you rushed to leave?

28:56.480 --> 28:57.400
There are other scores

28:57.400 --> 28:58.930
we need to settle together.

28:59.480 --> 29:00.550
Deputy Dean Nie.

29:03.200 --> 29:04.110
Do you remember

29:04.270 --> 29:05.110
these people?

29:07.240 --> 29:08.770
What is the meaning of this?

29:08.920 --> 29:10.240
Aren't you curious

29:10.720 --> 29:11.750
about how I collected

29:11.750 --> 29:12.950
so many of your works?

29:14.350 --> 29:15.160
While you were busy

29:15.160 --> 29:16.790
putting on a show on TV,

29:17.200 --> 29:18.790
Hou Qi and I visited

29:18.960 --> 29:20.890
all the colleagues you worked with

29:21.070 --> 29:22.920
after you joined
the Jiangcheng Design Institute—

29:22.920 --> 29:23.850
those who later resigned

29:23.850 --> 29:25.130
or were transferred—

29:25.640 --> 29:27.640
as well as your college classmates.

29:28.240 --> 29:29.270
They provided me

29:29.270 --> 29:30.930
with quite a few of your works.

29:38.400 --> 29:38.960
Ms. Xia,

29:39.640 --> 29:41.310
I didn't expect
that I wasn't the only one.

29:41.310 --> 29:43.110
There are so many other victims.

29:44.030 --> 29:44.960
Nie Weiguo

29:45.350 --> 29:47.240
has been throwing his weight around
for years.

29:47.240 --> 29:48.720
Too bad he met me this time.

29:50.160 --> 29:51.690
I'm going to skin him alive.

29:56.350 --> 29:57.440
This visit

29:57.830 --> 30:00.160
turned up more surprises than I expected.

30:01.960 --> 30:03.000
You have always

30:03.110 --> 30:04.350
abused your position

30:04.480 --> 30:05.740
to steal others' work,

30:06.110 --> 30:07.350
suppress the younger generation,

30:07.350 --> 30:09.880
and even sexually harass
female colleagues.

30:11.240 --> 30:12.880
[Complaint]

30:11.480 --> 30:12.030
This is the complaint

30:12.030 --> 30:13.560
they collectively signed.

30:13.750 --> 30:14.440
Today,

30:14.790 --> 30:15.750
I'm going to drag you,

30:15.750 --> 30:18.810
a pest in the architectural circle,
out into the light.

30:26.030 --> 30:26.960
Xia Xiaolan, you...

30:26.960 --> 30:27.640
Xia Xiaolan!

30:27.640 --> 30:28.200
What are you doing?

30:28.200 --> 30:28.830
This is too much!

30:28.830 --> 30:29.350
Hurry, get in the car!

30:29.350 --> 30:30.080
Xia Xiaolan!

30:30.200 --> 30:31.270
Hurry, get in the car!

30:31.270 --> 30:32.000
Xia Xiaolan!

30:32.640 --> 30:34.270
Xia Xiaolan, I won't let you off!

30:34.270 --> 30:35.350
Don't even think about surviving

30:35.350 --> 30:36.200
in this industry!

30:36.200 --> 30:36.960
Do you hear me?

30:36.960 --> 30:37.690
Xia Xiaolan!

30:45.510 --> 30:46.040
Let's go.

30:49.750 --> 30:50.280
Let's go.

31:28.920 --> 31:29.920
What are you up to?

31:30.720 --> 31:32.640
Are you keeping something from me?

31:32.640 --> 31:34.100
What happened to our deal?

31:34.160 --> 31:34.750
Why were there

31:34.750 --> 31:36.110
so many unnecessary moves?

31:36.110 --> 31:37.640
Were those moves targeting Du Zhaohui

31:37.640 --> 31:38.590
or someone else?

31:38.640 --> 31:40.100
Do I look like a fool to you?

31:41.310 --> 31:42.400
Second Young Master,

31:42.400 --> 31:44.000
put the gun down first, okay?

31:44.110 --> 31:45.790
I'll talk. I'll tell you everything.

31:45.790 --> 31:47.650
Just put the gun down first, okay?

31:54.000 --> 31:56.260
I didn't lie to you, Second Young Master.

31:56.400 --> 31:57.720
I said I'd join forces with you

31:57.720 --> 31:58.640
to deal with Du Zhaohui

31:58.640 --> 31:59.720
and win the competition
for the inheritance.

31:59.720 --> 32:01.380
That was absolutely not a lie.

32:02.400 --> 32:04.530
But the one who backed me into a corner,

32:05.270 --> 32:06.790
forcing me to follow Du Zhaohui's orders,

32:06.790 --> 32:08.250
the one who started it all,

32:09.310 --> 32:10.590
was Xia Xiaolan.

32:12.790 --> 32:14.440
Second Young Master, do you have time

32:14.440 --> 32:15.590
to hear a story?

32:16.070 --> 32:17.640
A story about a female college student

32:17.640 --> 32:19.590
who was framed as a fugitive.

32:23.790 --> 32:24.250
Come in.

32:26.230 --> 32:26.920
Second Young Master,

32:26.920 --> 32:28.920
here is the information you wanted.

32:39.050 --> 32:43.280
[Vivi after plastic surgery]
[Xia Ziyu before plastic surgery]

32:40.630 --> 32:41.510
It was Xia Xiaolan

32:41.510 --> 32:42.680
who did this to me.

32:43.490 --> 32:45.720
She has joined forces with Du Zhaohui now.

32:45.720 --> 32:47.250
They sink or swim together.

32:47.960 --> 32:49.110
O-Our goal

32:49.440 --> 32:50.440
is still the same,

32:51.240 --> 32:51.770
isn't it?

32:58.110 --> 32:59.400
For a woman whose face and name

32:59.400 --> 33:00.550
are both fake,

33:01.920 --> 33:03.720
how much of what she says is true?

33:07.440 --> 33:07.960
Mr. Liu.

33:08.310 --> 33:08.830
Ms. Xia.

33:09.490 --> 33:10.400
About what happened last time,

33:10.400 --> 33:11.530
I am terribly sorry.

33:12.070 --> 33:12.830
The other directors

33:12.830 --> 33:13.720
will be here soon.

33:13.720 --> 33:14.510
This way, please.

33:14.510 --> 33:15.510
Once we won the lawsuit,

33:15.510 --> 33:16.230
you transferred

33:16.230 --> 33:18.070
the final payment to us right away.

33:18.070 --> 33:19.110
That was a quick response.

33:19.110 --> 33:19.640
This way.

33:23.350 --> 33:24.400
Du Zhaohui.

33:24.720 --> 33:26.160
It's about the acceptance
of the Haihua Hotel.

33:26.160 --> 33:27.550
Why are you getting involved?

33:27.550 --> 33:29.200
Electronics City will open tomorrow.

33:29.200 --> 33:30.000
Are you ready?

33:30.340 --> 33:31.030
I'm ready.

33:31.160 --> 33:32.470
I'm waiting for your orders.

33:32.470 --> 33:33.200
After you finish the acceptance,

33:33.200 --> 33:35.400
I'll take you back to Electronics City?

33:35.920 --> 33:36.790
It's rare for you to come up with

33:36.790 --> 33:37.850
such a good excuse.

33:37.920 --> 33:38.270
Fine.

33:38.440 --> 33:39.690
I'll go with you then.

33:40.070 --> 33:40.640
Mr. Liu.

33:42.000 --> 33:42.400
Ms. Xia.

33:42.400 --> 33:43.680
Congratulations, Mr. Liu.

33:43.680 --> 33:44.280
Thank you.

33:45.720 --> 33:47.030
About what happened before,

33:47.030 --> 33:47.880
I'm sorry.

33:48.310 --> 33:50.400
My people didn't know any better.

33:51.420 --> 33:52.130
It's okay.

33:52.400 --> 33:54.720
Anyway, we have to do the acceptance
sooner or later.

33:54.720 --> 33:55.310
Yes, yes.

33:56.440 --> 33:56.970
Mr. Tang.

33:57.030 --> 33:57.560
How is it?

33:58.350 --> 33:58.960
Indeed.

33:59.640 --> 34:01.030
Compared to the renderings,

34:01.030 --> 34:02.400
it looks even more spectacular

34:02.400 --> 34:03.260
and beautiful.

34:04.000 --> 34:05.400
It really does look good.

34:07.400 --> 34:07.960
Ms. Xia,

34:09.000 --> 34:10.110
the edge of the pool ahead

34:10.110 --> 34:11.310
doesn't have a fence.

34:11.400 --> 34:12.030
Will there be any

34:12.030 --> 34:12.889
safety issues?

34:14.110 --> 34:16.150
That's the feature of an infinity pool.

34:16.150 --> 34:17.440
As for safety issues,

34:17.960 --> 34:20.489
it's clearly stated
in the project proposal.

34:20.590 --> 34:21.230
That's right.

34:21.230 --> 34:22.230
You didn't read it carefully.

34:22.230 --> 34:23.429
Look, it's very safe.

34:30.320 --> 34:31.230
It's okay. It's okay.

34:31.230 --> 34:32.000
Don't worry. Don't worry.

34:32.000 --> 34:32.800
It's safe.

34:32.880 --> 34:34.400
It's been tested. Very safe.

34:34.400 --> 34:35.659
Water brings fortune!

34:35.840 --> 34:37.280
-Great!
-Great!

34:37.590 --> 34:38.550
Electronics City will definitely

34:38.550 --> 34:39.900
be a great success tomorrow!

34:39.900 --> 34:40.670
We'll make a fortune!

34:40.670 --> 34:41.550
Make a fortune!

34:40.750 --> 34:44.520
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

34:45.650 --> 34:47.969
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

34:48.750 --> 34:51.050
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

34:53.750 --> 34:57.950
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

34:58.850 --> 35:01.360
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

35:01.380 --> 35:05.130
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

35:05.510 --> 35:06.360
Are you too nervous,

35:05.700 --> 35:08.090
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

35:06.360 --> 35:08.480
or did you catch a cold
from falling in the water?

35:08.480 --> 35:09.480
I guess I'm too nervous.

35:09.410 --> 35:11.980
♪ The dreams we dream in the day time ♪

35:10.030 --> 35:11.090
Also a bit excited.

35:11.670 --> 35:13.360
After all, I sold my car and house

35:12.820 --> 35:15.230
♪ Is passionate yet naive ♪

35:13.360 --> 35:14.070
to build this business,

35:14.070 --> 35:15.530
and it's finally opening.

35:15.920 --> 35:18.030
I just feel my blood pumping.

35:15.950 --> 35:20.830
♪ Our youth ♪

35:19.800 --> 35:20.800
Don't be nervous.

35:20.850 --> 35:24.380
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

35:21.070 --> 35:21.960
We've done

35:21.960 --> 35:23.480
everything we can ahead of time.

35:23.480 --> 35:24.630
Plus, with the publicity

35:24.400 --> 35:27.780
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

35:24.630 --> 35:25.960
that Nie Weiguo sent us,

35:26.030 --> 35:27.480
Chengrong Electronics City's title

35:27.480 --> 35:28.670
as No. 1 in Asia

35:27.960 --> 35:30.800
♪ We never give up ♪

35:29.000 --> 35:30.460
has already been hyped up.

35:31.360 --> 35:31.920
Yes.

35:31.570 --> 35:34.510
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

35:32.430 --> 35:33.440
Whether I stick my neck out

35:33.440 --> 35:34.550
or pull it back,
the blade will fall anyway.

35:34.550 --> 35:35.400
Whether I live or die,

35:34.880 --> 35:39.760
♪ That'd be enough ♪

35:35.510 --> 35:36.640
we'll see tomorrow.

35:39.600 --> 35:42.510
[Succession War Erupts
in Gangdao's Du Family]

35:59.230 --> 36:00.710
Do you know that in 3 days,

36:00.710 --> 36:02.640
it's your daddy's birthday party?

36:03.500 --> 36:04.620
I know, Mommy.

36:21.360 --> 36:22.160
Young Master.

36:22.550 --> 36:23.880
Your clothes are ready.

36:24.060 --> 36:25.570
I'll wake you up tomorrow.

36:26.540 --> 36:28.000
Good night, Young Master.

37:09.040 --> 37:09.510
[Asia's Largest Electronics Mall,
Chengrong Electronics City Plaza,]

37:09.510 --> 37:09.980
[to Open Grandly Tomorrow in Shengcheng]

37:17.110 --> 37:20.830
[Day 1 of Electronics City]

37:28.640 --> 37:31.890
[Chengrong Electronics City]

37:49.150 --> 37:50.410
Did I even set an alarm?

37:53.520 --> 37:55.550
Du Zhaohui's Electronics City is opening.

37:55.550 --> 37:57.280
Why am I more nervous than he is?

38:14.880 --> 38:15.510
Mr. Du,

38:15.710 --> 38:16.710
it's opening day.

38:16.760 --> 38:18.020
Will business be good?

38:18.480 --> 38:19.150
Business

38:19.190 --> 38:20.480
has to be good, right?

38:20.760 --> 38:22.760
Look at the sea of people outside.

38:22.840 --> 38:24.080
How could it not be booming?

38:24.080 --> 38:25.280
Listen to how they talk.

38:25.280 --> 38:27.210
Business will definitely be good.

38:28.030 --> 38:28.830
Good morning.

38:30.550 --> 38:31.840
Don't be nervous.

38:32.550 --> 38:33.350
Look outside.

38:34.190 --> 38:35.360
It's not even 8 o'clock yet,

38:35.360 --> 38:36.880
and there are already
so many people in line.

38:36.880 --> 38:38.010
Once the doors open,

38:38.110 --> 38:39.150
those lovely customers

38:39.150 --> 38:40.680
will rush in to spend money.

38:40.940 --> 38:41.870
What we need to do

38:42.030 --> 38:43.150
is serve them

38:43.150 --> 38:44.030
like kings.

38:44.800 --> 38:45.710
Let me be clear.

38:46.190 --> 38:47.030
If

38:47.030 --> 38:47.960
our service desk

38:48.070 --> 38:49.190
receives

38:49.480 --> 38:51.410
any service-related complaints,

38:51.590 --> 38:52.850
I will record them all.

38:53.000 --> 38:54.440
You'll be fined at the end of the month.

38:54.440 --> 38:55.110
Understood?

38:55.110 --> 38:55.510
Yes, yes.

38:55.510 --> 38:56.370
Remember that.

38:58.510 --> 38:59.320
I'll tell you

38:59.320 --> 39:00.230
some good news.

39:00.590 --> 39:02.360
To encourage customers to spend,

39:02.360 --> 39:03.890
we're having a grand opening sale.

39:03.890 --> 39:04.410
Today,

39:04.440 --> 39:05.710
spend at least 100 yuan

39:05.960 --> 39:07.190
at any stall,

39:07.710 --> 39:09.800
and they can enter the raffle!

39:10.880 --> 39:13.920
-Great!
-Great!

39:15.760 --> 39:18.030
-Great!
-Great!

39:18.440 --> 39:19.320
Friends,

39:19.550 --> 39:20.670
good news!

39:20.880 --> 39:23.480
Grand opening sale today!

39:23.840 --> 39:25.030
-Great!
-Great!

39:25.370 --> 39:26.680
Anyone who spends

39:26.710 --> 39:28.440
100 yuan or more

39:28.550 --> 39:30.880
can redeem a raffle ticket.

39:31.160 --> 39:32.370
Our first prize

39:32.400 --> 39:34.190
is a car!

39:34.280 --> 39:36.000
-Great!
-Great!

39:36.360 --> 39:38.960
Second prize is a motorcycle!

39:39.320 --> 39:40.000
-Great!
-Great!

39:40.000 --> 39:40.920
Third prize

39:40.940 --> 39:43.000
is a Wenquxing electronic dictionary!

39:43.000 --> 39:43.800
-Great!
-Great!

39:43.800 --> 39:45.760
And our lucky prize

39:45.840 --> 39:47.670
is a bag of laundry detergent!

39:47.670 --> 39:48.150
Not bad.

39:48.590 --> 39:50.110
Can we really win?

39:50.230 --> 39:52.160
You have to spend at least 100 yuan.

39:52.230 --> 39:53.150
If you spend 99 yuan,

39:53.150 --> 39:53.960
even one yuan short won't do,

39:53.960 --> 39:54.480
right?

39:54.510 --> 39:56.150
-That's right.
-Yes.

39:56.480 --> 39:58.320
Giving away a car in a draw?

39:58.400 --> 39:59.800
It's not a scam, is it?

39:59.920 --> 40:01.590
You probably have to buy something

40:01.590 --> 40:02.710
before you can draw.

40:02.710 --> 40:03.800
Right, right.

40:03.840 --> 40:06.570
Quiet down, everyone.
Listen to the rules first.

40:06.760 --> 40:07.230
First,

40:07.450 --> 40:08.970
this lucky draw event

40:09.000 --> 40:10.660
is hosted by Chengrong Plaza.

40:10.850 --> 40:12.810
After redeeming your ticket,

40:12.840 --> 40:14.440
make sure to keep it safe.

40:14.750 --> 40:16.480
Damaged tickets are invalid.

40:16.510 --> 40:17.840
Fake tickets are invalid.

40:17.840 --> 40:18.400
Second,

40:18.440 --> 40:20.510
for every 100 yuan spent
in a single transaction,

40:20.510 --> 40:22.150
you can redeem a raffle ticket.

40:22.150 --> 40:23.930
100 yuan gets you one ticket.

40:23.960 --> 40:25.920
200 yuan gets you 2.

40:26.110 --> 40:27.280
And so on.

40:27.720 --> 40:28.640
For example,

40:28.670 --> 40:29.550
if a customer

40:29.590 --> 40:31.480
spends 398 yuan,

40:31.510 --> 40:33.760
they can redeem 3 raffle tickets

40:34.000 --> 40:36.230
and get 3 chances to draw.

40:36.510 --> 40:38.150
But spending 398 yuan

40:38.150 --> 40:38.880
for 3 draws

40:38.880 --> 40:40.360
seems a bit of a waste, right?

40:40.360 --> 40:41.360
So what do you do?

40:42.030 --> 40:43.630
Add 2 more yuan...

40:44.510 --> 40:46.710
Where can you find
a 2-yuan item in Electronics City?

40:46.710 --> 40:47.800
You want to round up the sum,

40:47.800 --> 40:48.920
but then you go over.

40:48.920 --> 40:49.840
Then with the extra amount,

40:49.840 --> 40:50.360
you wonder if you can

40:50.360 --> 40:51.350
reach 500.

40:51.840 --> 40:53.550
Before you know it, the merchant

40:53.550 --> 40:54.610
has led you astray.

40:54.630 --> 40:56.420
This will be a popular trick
in the future, right?

40:56.420 --> 40:58.540
Attorney Zhou, you really are smart.

40:58.670 --> 40:59.270
Of course.

40:59.920 --> 41:01.280
It won't just be popular in the future.

41:01.280 --> 41:02.840
It will also be used for scams.

41:02.840 --> 41:04.960
Spend a few more yuan for another ticket

41:04.960 --> 41:06.890
and another chance at the jackpot.

41:07.630 --> 41:09.280
But you definitely won't win.

41:09.280 --> 41:11.080
But Du Zhaohui wouldn't do that.

41:11.230 --> 41:12.360
These prizes mean nothing

41:12.360 --> 41:13.110
to him.

41:13.670 --> 41:15.030
However, we need to arrange

41:15.030 --> 41:16.290
the timing of the wins.

41:16.320 --> 41:17.070
Otherwise, if the first prize is drawn

41:17.070 --> 41:18.070
early in the morning,

41:18.070 --> 41:18.800
the later customers

41:18.800 --> 41:19.930
will lose interest.

41:21.000 --> 41:21.860
Attorney Zhou,

41:22.000 --> 41:23.260
do you want to draw one?

41:23.960 --> 41:24.550
Sure.

41:24.920 --> 41:25.280
Okay.

41:25.550 --> 41:26.750
I'll set it up for you.

41:27.360 --> 41:27.880
Alright,

41:27.880 --> 41:29.230
it's almost time.

41:29.480 --> 41:31.070
Let's look forward to

41:31.110 --> 41:33.910
the grand opening
of Chengrong Electronics City!

41:56.760 --> 41:58.590
Open the doors and welcome the guests!
